room_title: Escape room "Submerged" by Hint Hunter Puzzle Rooms in Biloxi
room_address: 10253 D'Iberville Blvd Suite B D'Iberville, MS 39540
room_description: The submarine slowly descends to the bottom of the ocean. Only the brave will step out and explore the galleon shipwreck site. Legends say that a monstrous sea creature guards a mystical relic in the deep dark waters. Can you locate the artifact and reach the surface before you run out of oxygen?
